m\": 323, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It reflected higher scores in four out his six dives from the preliminary entry but was not good enough to qualify for Paris yet.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999987251627712, \"rank\": 1.2748387693026893e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I am a bit disappointed with the result, because I knew I could finish higher up, but I am still proud of how far I have come from last year and hopefully I can improve again next year.\\\"\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Passmore will return to the boards on Saturday for the Mixed 3M Synchro final with Clare Cryan.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Cryan\", \"score\": 0.8620657357163883, \"rank\": 0.16000000000000425, \"text\": \"Clare Cryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Cryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Cryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cryan will be the final individual Irish diver in action in Doha when she takes to the 3M Springboard on Thursday.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998956034644433, \"rank\": 0.00010305652168517433, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 4.0028964073819785e-12, \"text\": \"Doha\"